<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Riemannian_geometry&action=edit&section=12.php.html" title="Edit section: Literature">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Literature">Literature</span></h2>
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation Journal"><a href="Kleinert" title="Kleinert" class="mw-redirect">Hagen Kleinert</a> (1989). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://users.physik.fu-berlin.de/~kleinert/kleiner_reb1/contents2.html"><i>Gauge Fields in Condensed Matter Vol II</i></a>. pp.&#160;743–1440<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://users.physik.fu-berlin.de/~kleinert/kleiner_reb1/contents2.html">http://users.physik.fu-berlin.de/~kleinert/kleiner_reb1/contents2.html</a></span>.</span></span></li>
